## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of publicly accessible information and the inherent complexity of tax laws, which can vary significantly by jurisdiction. Additionally, the strategies discussed are subject to change as tax laws evolve. The report focuses on general strategies and may not cover all possible loopholes exploited by the super-rich.